data.description: LAKEFRONT! This beautiful 2 bedroom 2 bath lakefront home is located in the desirable Quail Lakes area. Once you enter through your private gated courtyard, this home boasts soaring vaulted ceilings and a formal dining area with built-in buffet storage. The spacious living room has a cozy gas fireplace for cooler weather. Enjoy the lake views from the large windows inside the home, have coffee on your patio or relax on the dock. Large master bedroom includes plenty of closet space. Too many items to list, come see this beauty for yourself!
